com.hazelcast.cache.impl

Class CachePortableHook

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.cache.impl.CachePortableHook
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PortableHook

    public class CachePortableHook
extends Object
implements PortableHook
    CachePortableHook contains all the ID hooks for classes used inside the JCache framework which implement Portable. JCache client request implementations are mapped in here.

    This factory class is used by internal portable serialization.
